title: Speculation Fills The Void
description:
Charly, KMart, and Elle want to remind you that just because you win a game doesn't mean you have our full support... Colts we're looking at you. Then, we need y'all to listen up and stop making false equivalencies when it comes to Ime Udoka... the ladies dive in and it gets heated.
